name: Axolotl Game (kiaraaa)
description:
My game is about an Axolotl that has to collect keys in order to get to the next level.

The red squares are the enemies and if they collide with the player then the game would restart. 

Once you collect all the keys from level one click the number nine to go to the next level and once you have collected all keys from level 2 click the number 8 to go the next level.
